name: New Shoreham (Block Island) Residents POD
address: 10 Beach Ave, New Shoreham Rhode Island, 02807
info: This clinic is for people 18 years of age or older who need their SECOND DOSE of MODERNA vaccine (which needs to be at least 4 weeks after your first dose).  Please do not register for it if you are looking for a first dose and are unable to travel off the island in four weeks to get your corresponding second dose, as there will be no second dose Moderna on the island four weeks from this date.
special: If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.

name: Dunkin Donuts Center POD
address: 1 La Salle Square, Providence Rhode Island, 02903
info: ●●● ENGLISH: This clinic is offering the Moderna COVID-19 vaccine which is for people age 18 and older only. This clinic is for people who are age 18 and older who live, work, or go to school in Rhode Island. For clinic directions and parking information, visit https://health.ri.gov/vaccinesiteinfo. ●●● ESPAÑOL: Esta clínica ofrece la vacuna Moderna contra COVID-19 que es para personas con 18 años o más solamente. Esta clínica recibe personas mayores de 18 años que viven, trabajan o asisten a clases en Rhode Island. Para direcciones de llegar a la clínica o información de estacionamiento, visite la siguiente página: https://health.ri.gov/vaccinesiteinfo. ●●● PORTUGUÊS: Esta clínica está a oferecer a vacina COVID-19 da Moderna, que é apenas para pessoas com 18 anos ou mais. Esta clínica é para pessoas com 18 anos de idade ou mais que morem, trabalhem ou frequentem escolas em Rhode Island. Para direções e informações de estacionamento a clínica, visite https://health.ri.gov/vaccinesiteinfo.
special: If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.
